<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - Cowors</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .security-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #b91c1c;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .security-tips {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-tips h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .reset-code {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border: 2px dashed #9ca3af;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Cowors</div>
            <div class="security-icon">üîê</div>
            <h1 class="title">Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <span class="highlight">{{firstName}}</span>,</p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Alert:</strong> We received a request to reset the password for your Cowors account.</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                <p><strong>Request Time:</strong> {{requestTime}}</p>
                {{#if ipAddress}}
                <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if resetUrl}}
                <p><strong>To reset your password, click the button below:</strong></p>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta-button">Reset My Password</a>
                </div>
                
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
                <p style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">{{resetUrl}}</p>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if resetCode}}
                <p><strong>Alternatively, use this verification code:</strong></p>
                
                <div class="reset-code">
                    {{resetCode}}
                </div>
                
                <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">Enter this code on the password reset page</p>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <p><strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong> This {{#if resetCode}}code{{else}}link{{/if}} will expire in <strong>{{expiryTime}}</strong> for security reasons.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong>üõ°Ô∏è Didn't request this?</strong></p>
                <p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged, and your account is secure.</p>
                <p>However, if you're concerned about unauthorized access, we recommend:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Changing your password immediately</li>
                    <li>Reviewing your recent account activity</li>
                    <li>Contacting our support team</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h4>üîí Password Security Tips:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Use a strong password:</strong> At least 8 characters with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
                    <li><strong>Make it unique:</strong> Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
                    <li><strong>Consider a password manager:</strong> To generate and store secure passwords</li>
                    <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication:</strong> Add an extra layer of security</li>
                    <li><strong>Keep it private:</strong> Never share your password with anyone</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you continue to have trouble accessing your account or have any security concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Stay secure,</p>
            <p><strong>The Cowors Security Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Password reset request for {{email}}</p>
            <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Cowors. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>